    "description": "We at Cello Asia Pacific Associates are looking for an experienced Visual Merchandiser based out of Agra. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Cello Asia Pacific Associates:\nCello Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n• Train and motivate the sales team to deliver excellent service\n• Monitor inventory levels and coordinate replenishment activities\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n• Manage shrinkage and reduce stock discrepancies\n• Coordinate with the supply chain team for timely stock delivery\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in POS Systems\n• Proficiency in Loyalty Programs\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Shrinkage Control\n• Proficiency in E-commerce Integration\n• Proficiency in CRM\n• Proficiency in Omnichannel Retail\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Learning & development budget\n• Referral bonus program\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Agra, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Cello Asia Pacific Associates!",
